--> Amazon quick site or Grafana for dashboard visualization

--> SNS this is used for notification (Simple Notification Service)
	Republishing and MQTT message
	Sending an Amazon SNS notification
	Storing the data into Dynamo DB table
	Formatting a notification by using an AWS lambda function
	
--> Creating Policy
	1. Search for IAM 
	2. Create a new policy
	3. Choose IoT in Service and also tick all service
	4. Expand Resources and select the All resources 

